    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>ginger</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>honey</strong>, <strong>hoisin sauce</strong> and<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>your <strong>five-spice</strong> to a large bowl</p><p>Add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>water</strong> and give everything a good mix up - this is your <strong>marinade</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>pork loin steak[s]</strong> to the marinade and set aside</p>",
      "order": 3,
